WEBVTT

00:00:00.160 --> 00:00:02.470
Hello everybody. I'm Brandon Biggs, and

00:00:02.480 --> 00:00:04.789
this is Diana Biggs, and welcome to

00:00:04.799 --> 00:00:07.590
today's broadcast. I

00:00:07.600 --> 00:00:10.270
told you all for my birthday one

00:00:10.280 --> 00:00:12.470
year, the Lord said, 'I want to give you

00:00:12.480 --> 00:00:15.350
a little present.'I was in

00:00:15.360 --> 00:00:17.990
prayer, and I was just seeking Him.

00:00:18.000 --> 00:00:19.750
He said, 'I want to show you

00:00:19.750 --> 00:00:19.760
something.'All

00:00:19.760 --> 00:00:21.830
of a sudden, I was

00:00:21.840 --> 00:00:23.670
interceding for my

00:00:23.680 --> 00:00:26.550
birthday, and I was seeing in

00:00:26.560 --> 00:00:30.029
the spirit. I saw these beautiful

00:00:30.039 --> 00:00:33.110
mountains with snow caps on the top

00:00:33.120 --> 00:00:36.430
of them. They looked like the Swiss

00:00:36.430 --> 00:00:36.440
Alps—absolutely

00:00:36.440 --> 00:00:39.030
beautiful mountains.

00:00:39.040 --> 00:00:42.229
There was a green valley with

00:00:42.239 --> 00:00:45.190
grass that was just the most beautiful,

00:00:45.190 --> 00:00:45.200
translucent-looking

00:00:45.200 --> 00:00:47.750
grass. It was

00:00:47.760 --> 00:00:50.709
gorgeous grass with flowers, like a

00:00:50.719 --> 00:00:53.110
meadow with butterflies. It

00:00:53.120 --> 00:00:55.590
was just the most beautiful backdrop

00:00:55.600 --> 00:00:57.270
with these mountains, a

00:00:57.280 --> 00:00:59.590
lake, and this beautiful scenery all

00:00:59.600 --> 00:01:03.510
around. Diana was doing cartwheels, and

00:01:03.520 --> 00:01:06.670
the Lord said, 'This is moments after the

00:01:06.670 --> 00:01:06.680
Rapture.'We

00:01:06.680 --> 00:01:10.270
were standing there in

00:01:10.280 --> 00:01:13.190
heaven. I was a young man; I looked a

00:01:13.200 --> 00:01:17.310
lot younger and I had hair. I had a

00:01:17.320 --> 00:01:19.910
glorified body, and Diana had her

00:01:19.920 --> 00:01:22.710
glorified body. She said, 'Brandon,

00:01:22.720 --> 00:01:25.190
we made it! We made it!'She was

00:01:25.200 --> 00:01:27.429
doing cartwheels, and she was

00:01:27.439 --> 00:01:29.350
just rejoicing and running through this

00:01:29.360 --> 00:01:31.590
meadow. It was green all around,

00:01:31.590 --> 00:01:31.600
with

00:01:31.600 --> 00:01:33.990
a beautiful green hill, and

00:01:34.000 --> 00:01:35.830
she was running and

00:01:35.840 --> 00:01:38.230
rejoicing. It was just so beautiful. I

00:01:38.230 --> 00:01:38.240
was

00:01:38.240 --> 00:01:41.030
breathing in

00:01:44.000 --> 00:01:46.789
the beautiful atmosphere of heaven for

00:01:46.799 --> 00:01:48.630
the very first time.

00:01:48.640 --> 00:01:50.149
Whenever you get

00:01:50.149 --> 00:01:50.159
to

00:01:50.159 --> 00:01:52.550
a hotel room or

00:01:52.560 --> 00:01:54.069
go to a place on vacation where you've never been,

00:01:56.320 --> 00:01:57.990
you want to see

00:01:58.000 --> 00:01:59.670
everything and all the sights around

00:01:59.670 --> 00:01:59.680
because

00:01:59.680 --> 00:02:01.990
you're just excited to be there.

00:02:02.000 --> 00:02:04.950
Multiply that

00:02:04.950 --> 00:02:04.960
by

00:02:04.960 --> 00:02:07.350
a billion. That's

00:02:07.360 --> 00:02:10.949
what this felt like: we made it. And the

00:02:10.959 --> 00:02:13.030
temperature—I

00:02:13.040 --> 00:02:15.270
remember I could

00:02:15.280 --> 00:02:17.430
feel it—it was like I was

00:02:17.440 --> 00:02:19.990
there. The atmosphere was

00:02:19.990 --> 00:02:20.000
about

00:02:20.000 --> 00:02:22.869
65 to 70 degrees. It wasn't hot, but it

00:02:22.879 --> 00:02:24.949
wasn't cold. It was a perfect

00:02:24.959 --> 00:02:27.830
temperature.

00:02:27.840 --> 00:02:30.150
Everything was perfect, and you could see

00:02:30.160 --> 00:02:32.470
those mountains, and

00:02:32.480 --> 00:02:35.350
it was just beautiful. I want to

00:02:35.360 --> 00:02:38.869
tell you all, heaven is a real place.

00:02:38.879 --> 00:02:41.910
Most people go, 'Well, is

00:02:41.910 --> 00:02:41.920
it?'No,

00:02:41.920 --> 00:02:46.229
I've seen it. I've been there. I've seen

00:02:46.229 --> 00:02:46.239
it—it

00:02:46.239 --> 00:02:50.350
is a massive,

00:02:50.350 --> 00:02:50.360
planet-like

00:02:50.360 --> 00:02:53.910
place. It is humongous. When I was

00:02:53.920 --> 00:02:56.150
taken back and I was coming to the Earth,

00:02:56.160 --> 00:03:00.309
it was in a ripple,

00:03:00.319 --> 00:03:03.030
how He had it hidden.

00:03:06.080 --> 00:03:08.949
It was a massive

00:03:08.949 --> 00:03:08.959
place,

00:03:08.959 --> 00:03:11.390
like three times the size of

00:03:11.400 --> 00:03:15.830
Jupiter, and there

00:03:15.840 --> 00:03:19.589
was no darkness at all. Everything

00:03:19.599 --> 00:03:21.630
was glowing. There

00:03:21.630 --> 00:03:21.640
were

00:03:21.640 --> 00:03:23.869
no

00:03:23.879 --> 00:03:27.229
shadows because there is no

00:03:27.239 --> 00:03:30.110
darkness. How do you explain that to

00:03:30.120 --> 00:03:34.390
somebody? Because

00:03:34.390 --> 00:03:34.400
all we

00:03:34.400 --> 00:03:36.949
know are

00:03:36.949 --> 00:03:36.959
shadows—there are

00:03:36.959 --> 00:03:38.789
shadows

00:03:38.799 --> 00:03:43.350
on the table. But there, there is no darkness.

00:03:43.360 --> 00:03:44.830
Everything is

00:03:44.840 --> 00:03:47.589
beautiful. Then one day I was

00:03:47.599 --> 00:03:49.509
praying, and the Lord told me to tell you

00:03:49.519 --> 00:03:51.270
all about this. That's how that

00:03:51.280 --> 00:03:53.430
basically ended; He allowed me to see

00:03:53.440 --> 00:03:55.270
Diana doing the cartwheels, and I was

00:03:55.280 --> 00:03:58.470
just looking over the horizon

00:03:58.470 --> 00:03:58.480
at

00:03:58.480 --> 00:04:01.670
the beauty of

00:04:01.680 --> 00:04:04.229
an area of heaven. I don't know if my house

00:04:04.239 --> 00:04:05.990
was nearby there or not, but I

00:04:06.000 --> 00:04:09.110
wouldn't mind it in that green valley,

00:04:09.110 --> 00:04:09.120
by

00:04:09.120 --> 00:04:11.190
that lake, and those mountains with

00:04:11.200 --> 00:04:13.630
the snow

00:04:13.630 --> 00:04:13.640
tops.

00:04:13.640 --> 00:04:16.229
The things He has for every single

00:04:16.239 --> 00:04:19.030
one of you! If you only knew how much He

00:04:19.040 --> 00:04:20.949
loves you. If you just read

00:04:20.959 --> 00:04:22.950
your Bible and look at whenever it says

00:04:22.960 --> 00:04:24.990
that God is

00:04:25.000 --> 00:04:29.110
love, God loves you. He gave His

00:04:29.120 --> 00:04:32.070
one and only begotten Son, that whosoever

00:04:32.070 --> 00:04:32.080
believes

00:04:32.080 --> 00:04:34.550
in Him should

00:04:34.560 --> 00:04:36.909
not perish but have everlasting

00:04:36.919 --> 00:04:39.510
life. Every single one of us has an

00:04:39.520 --> 00:04:42.150
opportunity today to say yes to Jesus

00:04:42.160 --> 00:04:45.270
and no to hell. Every single one of us.

00:04:45.280 --> 00:04:47.189
You have a hell to

00:04:47.199 --> 00:04:49.270
shun and a heaven to gain.

00:04:49.280 --> 00:04:51.430
Rodney

00:04:51.430 --> 00:04:51.440
Howard-Browne

00:04:51.440 --> 00:04:53.830
talks about that.

00:04:53.840 --> 00:04:56.150
But I just want to encourage you all

00:04:56.160 --> 00:04:58.629
that when we go in the

00:04:58.639 --> 00:05:01.909
Rapture... I was praying one day,

00:05:01.919 --> 00:05:03.990
just like I always

00:05:04.000 --> 00:05:06.950
do. I said, 'Lord,

00:05:06.960 --> 00:05:08.710
what are you up to today? What is going

00:05:08.720 --> 00:05:10.390
on with you?'—just being personal with

00:05:10.400 --> 00:05:12.390
Him. And He said, 'Brandon, I'm going to

00:05:12.400 --> 00:05:16.390
show you what I'm

00:05:16.390 --> 00:05:16.400
doing.'He

00:05:16.400 --> 00:05:19.749
opened up a portal above me. It was a

00:05:19.759 --> 00:05:21.830
beautiful portal, and Jesus looked out

00:05:21.840 --> 00:05:23.110
through that portal and said,

00:05:23.120 --> 00:05:24.950
'I'm going to show you what I'm doing

00:05:24.950 --> 00:05:24.960
today.'Just

00:05:24.960 --> 00:05:26.469
like that, right

00:05:26.479 --> 00:05:27.870
up

00:05:27.880 --> 00:05:31.189
here. All of a sudden, I went into

00:05:31.199 --> 00:05:34.070
that portal in the spirit.

00:05:34.080 --> 00:05:35.510
I went

00:05:35.520 --> 00:05:38.870
into that portal that He opened up above

00:05:38.880 --> 00:05:42.510
our living

00:05:42.520 --> 00:05:45.670
room, and I could see millions of plate

00:05:45.680 --> 00:05:47.870
settings

00:05:51.759 --> 00:05:55.909
that stretched forever,

00:05:55.919 --> 00:05:58.790
lined up on these

00:05:58.800 --> 00:06:02.070
beautiful tables. I'm talking beautiful wood tables with a gloss on them, not cheap plastic tables from

00:06:02.080 --> 00:06:06.909
Walmart.

00:06:09.840 --> 00:06:13.029
Each one of them had a name

00:06:13.039 --> 00:06:17.990
tag

00:06:18.000 --> 00:06:21.830
prepared for each one of us. There was a doily

00:06:21.840 --> 00:06:25.590
in the middle, and beautiful fine china

00:06:25.590 --> 00:06:25.600
with

00:06:25.600 --> 00:06:30.150
golden lace around it.

00:06:30.160 --> 00:06:32.909
It was all

00:06:32.919 --> 00:06:36.790
specifically designed for you out of the

00:06:36.800 --> 00:06:39.749
desires of your heart—the things that

00:06:39.759 --> 00:06:42.950
you find beautiful and attractive, things

00:06:42.960 --> 00:06:45.749
where

00:06:45.759 --> 00:06:48.070
you go, 'Wow, that makes me so happy,

00:06:48.080 --> 00:06:50.070
Lord. Thank you for that.'Because God

00:06:50.080 --> 00:06:51.870
loves beautiful

00:06:51.880 --> 00:06:55.270
things. He is meticulous in everything

00:06:55.280 --> 00:06:58.150
He does; He cares about every single

00:06:58.160 --> 00:07:00.390
detail concerning every single one of

00:07:00.400 --> 00:07:05.029
you. Even your name is on that

00:07:05.039 --> 00:07:07.430
name card in the

00:07:07.440 --> 00:07:10.629
center of those plates. On my plate,

00:07:10.639 --> 00:07:12.790
what He was showing me, I saw Brandon

00:07:12.790 --> 00:07:12.800
Biggs

00:07:12.800 --> 00:07:17.629
and I saw a

00:07:17.629 --> 00:07:17.639
translucent-looking

00:07:17.639 --> 00:07:21.189
lily plate that was

00:07:21.199 --> 00:07:23.589
beautiful because I love flowers.

00:07:23.599 --> 00:07:27.749
I am a flower person; I love

00:07:27.759 --> 00:07:30.230
landscaping and flowers. I could spend

00:07:30.240 --> 00:07:32.469
hours just pulling weeds

00:07:32.469 --> 00:07:32.479
and

00:07:32.479 --> 00:07:35.589
making things look beautiful. I love

00:07:35.599 --> 00:07:39.029
flowers of all His

00:07:39.029 --> 00:07:39.039
creation—it's

00:07:39.039 --> 00:07:42.350
a big deal for me.

00:07:42.360 --> 00:07:44.510
I

00:07:44.520 --> 00:07:48.629
saw that my plate was a lily,

00:07:48.639 --> 00:07:50.150
and it was pink and beautiful.

00:07:50.160 --> 00:07:52.469
Then the one next to me was

00:07:52.469 --> 00:07:52.479
white-looking

00:07:52.479 --> 00:07:55.510
china, and

00:07:55.520 --> 00:07:59.990
I saw

00:08:00.000 --> 00:08:02.230
the

00:08:02.240 --> 00:08:04.390
settings of the forks. Then there

00:08:04.390 --> 00:08:04.400
were

00:08:04.400 --> 00:08:08.790
some plates down over here that had

00:08:08.800 --> 00:08:11.830
chopsticks in them because

00:08:11.840 --> 00:08:14.150
not everybody likes to use a fork.

00:08:14.160 --> 00:08:15.830
That's neat! There are some people

00:08:15.830 --> 00:08:15.840
who

00:08:15.840 --> 00:08:18.070
like chopsticks. They might say, 'Well,

00:08:18.080 --> 00:08:20.150
what are we going to eat?'I don't know.

00:08:20.150 --> 00:08:20.160
The

00:08:20.160 --> 00:08:21.749
Bible says the marriage supper of the

00:08:21.759 --> 00:08:23.110
Lamb. What is that? I don't know. Maybe

00:08:23.120 --> 00:08:25.110
we'll eat lamb—I have no idea, folks. I

00:08:25.120 --> 00:08:27.510
just know that there's a reception, and I

00:08:27.520 --> 00:08:29.189
saw the reception

00:08:31.919 --> 00:08:33.870
He was preparing for the

00:08:33.880 --> 00:08:37.350
bride, and it was beautiful. There

00:08:37.360 --> 00:08:39.750
was lace and beautiful things throughout

00:08:39.760 --> 00:08:43.190
the trees, and there

00:08:45.269 --> 00:08:45.279
were

00:08:47.279 --> 00:08:50.310
twinkle lights in that lace,

00:08:50.320 --> 00:08:53.190
powered by Holy Spirit power,

00:08:53.200 --> 00:08:55.110
I guess. They were like

00:08:56.480 --> 00:08:59.590
little lightning bugs

00:08:59.600 --> 00:09:02.470
all inside of this lace, and it was

00:09:02.480 --> 00:09:04.310
wrapped in tulle in these

00:09:04.320 --> 00:09:06.710
humongous oak trees, like weeping

00:09:06.720 --> 00:09:09.269
willows. You know how you see those down

00:09:09.279 --> 00:09:10.790
in New Orleans where the moss

00:09:10.790 --> 00:09:10.800
is

00:09:10.800 --> 00:09:13.350
dangling out of those trees? It

00:09:13.360 --> 00:09:14.949
was like that, but there was

00:09:14.959 --> 00:09:18.710
gorgeous-looking

00:09:18.720 --> 00:09:20.949
lace in this massive tree next to the

00:09:20.959 --> 00:09:25.269
table. Beautiful! It was a ginormous

00:09:25.279 --> 00:09:26.949
tree, not some skinny tree.

00:09:26.959 --> 00:09:29.190
I'm talking about trees

00:09:29.190 --> 00:09:29.200
with

00:09:29.200 --> 00:09:31.509
huge trunks.

00:09:31.519 --> 00:09:33.590
They were all in the

00:09:33.600 --> 00:09:35.430
atmosphere above, wrapped in

00:09:35.430 --> 00:09:35.440
tulle with

00:09:35.440 --> 00:09:37.190
little

00:09:37.200 --> 00:09:39.550
twinkle lights. I could see all of

00:09:39.550 --> 00:09:39.560
that.

00:09:39.560 --> 00:09:43.030
Then they had flower

00:09:43.040 --> 00:09:45.230
arrangements on all the

00:09:45.240 --> 00:09:48.470
tables in crystal

00:09:48.470 --> 00:09:48.480
vases—beautiful

00:09:48.480 --> 00:09:50.949
things that

00:09:52.959 --> 00:09:55.509
fanned out with

00:09:55.519 --> 00:09:57.430
all kinds of beautiful purples,

00:09:57.440 --> 00:10:00.070
greens,

00:10:00.080 --> 00:10:01.990
baby's breath,

00:10:02.000 --> 00:10:05.030
and beautiful

00:10:05.040 --> 00:10:08.470
lavender and pink flowers.

00:10:08.480 --> 00:10:12.070
It was done so perfectly. All of it.

00:10:12.080 --> 00:10:14.389
And they were on all the tables and all

00:10:14.399 --> 00:10:16.710
the doilies and all of it. It was

00:10:16.720 --> 00:10:20.550
just so like a beautiful, beautiful

00:10:20.560 --> 00:10:21.790
wedding

00:10:21.800 --> 00:10:24.509
reception. And

00:10:24.519 --> 00:10:26.710
then I don't want to cut it too short

00:10:26.720 --> 00:10:28.630
because I always try to tell y'all the

00:10:28.640 --> 00:10:30.310
things about it, and sometimes I add more

00:10:30.320 --> 00:10:32.310
to it because I'm like, you

00:10:32.320 --> 00:10:35.590
know, why hurry? Why hurry? You know, if

00:10:35.600 --> 00:10:36.870
you want to listen to it, fine. If you

00:10:36.880 --> 00:10:39.829
don't, fine. Fast forward it. But it was

00:10:39.839 --> 00:10:42.310
just beautiful, and it was, as far

00:10:42.320 --> 00:10:44.949
as I could see, plates and things ready

00:10:44.959 --> 00:10:46.710
for the people, and they were all okay.

00:10:46.720 --> 00:10:48.790
So one table setting was like

00:10:48.800 --> 00:10:51.350
this, and the table was all like an old

00:10:51.350 --> 00:10:51.360
English-looking

00:10:51.360 --> 00:10:53.829
table, like what you

00:10:53.839 --> 00:10:56.550
would see in a royal castle, like for the

00:10:56.560 --> 00:10:59.509
queen, because the table was all

00:10:59.519 --> 00:11:01.829
like it was all cut out like from a

00:11:01.839 --> 00:11:04.389
single piece of wood. It wasn't like, you

00:11:04.399 --> 00:11:05.750
know, like we make our

00:11:05.750 --> 00:11:05.760
cheap-looking

00:11:05.760 --> 00:11:07.829
tables today. We're talking it looked

00:11:07.839 --> 00:11:10.870
like Prince George, like,

00:11:10.880 --> 00:11:13.110
you know, like the old beds.

00:11:13.120 --> 00:11:15.030
It looked like the legs on that

00:11:15.040 --> 00:11:18.470
table were all kind of engraved wood.

00:11:20.279 --> 00:11:22.870
Engraved, and so you could see

00:11:22.880 --> 00:11:25.110
it, but it was a darker wood, a lighter

00:11:25.120 --> 00:11:26.790
wood, and then a darker wood. And it

00:11:26.800 --> 00:11:29.430
flushed in like it was just like

00:11:29.430 --> 00:11:29.440
marble-looking

00:11:29.440 --> 00:11:32.389
wood. And it was gorgeous.

00:11:32.399 --> 00:11:35.630
And then the Lord showed

00:11:35.640 --> 00:11:39.670
me the tables, but they went table,

00:11:39.680 --> 00:11:43.509
aisle, table, aisle, and every single

00:11:43.519 --> 00:11:45.269
person was just ready for them. And it

00:11:45.279 --> 00:11:48.470
went as far as you could see. I mean,

00:11:48.480 --> 00:11:50.150
you know, we're talking millions of

00:11:50.160 --> 00:11:52.069
people here. I don't know if it's by

00:11:52.079 --> 00:11:54.630
shift or whatever. You come by the

00:11:54.640 --> 00:11:56.470
generation. I don't know. How are you

00:11:56.480 --> 00:11:58.230
going to have the reception for all

00:11:58.240 --> 00:12:00.069
those people? But heaven's huge.

00:12:00.079 --> 00:12:02.230
But I'm just saying it just, you know,

00:12:02.240 --> 00:12:05.509
for what I could see, it was for

00:12:05.519 --> 00:12:07.509
hundreds of thousands. I don't know. I

00:12:07.519 --> 00:12:10.069
don't tell that it was millions of

00:12:10.079 --> 00:12:12.389
places for what I could see, but

00:12:12.399 --> 00:12:16.230
it was amazing. And then I could see the

00:12:16.240 --> 00:12:20.230
English Tudor houses.

00:12:20.240 --> 00:12:24.230
Oh, yeah, the old cobblestone homes. And

00:12:24.240 --> 00:12:26.350
see, in

00:12:26.360 --> 00:12:29.509
that generation of people, whether it's

00:12:29.519 --> 00:12:32.069
1700s or whatever, that was their

00:12:32.079 --> 00:12:35.030
heart's desire. The Bible says that he's

00:12:35.040 --> 00:12:36.949
making a mansion for every single one of

00:12:36.959 --> 00:12:39.430
